{"tid":2018754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日第一日返工已經咁....","createTime":"2020-05-15T21:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T06:03:43.000Z","uid":358481,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5943ae3932800214aadbad41c344c9c6e95ba628","tid":2018754,"uid":358481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:05:21.000Z","msg":"之前從來未用過警棍，第一轉就要打尻班學生，頂硬上，係就係慢小小，去完一轉，手已經好硬，第二轉8棍已經手軟，行唔到咁，師兄睇量我，俾我打6棍先，勉強頂到，好不容易先捱到中午飯，去左沙田一間茶餐廳到食，咁送左例湯黎， 攞起隻匙羹，我屌，提唔能起，右手已經硬能曬，我要用個頭壓低黎飲湯，心諗，仆街喇，重有半日點捱，好，食完飯，又推過，又熱又曬，已經出到沒曬汗，我知再唔飲水，一定會死，我愉雞經過藍店買支野飲，一野飲曬都唔夠，但起碼有返汗出，到岩岩放工時，佢地問我返唔返第二日，我話唔返，第日就辭職，好敬佩佢地，份工真係唔簡單"},{"pid":"9f9508ccca96c685d760ebd1d31da37d461e65c4","tid":2018754,"uid":41490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"e4986ad88e8295baef82043e90193962c4b75a05","tid":2018754,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d700a39f1f08e0cedc7e2262920e97fa4075da","tid":2018754,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:03:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182cb9d2cf774a077d408226d47669a1f69870bd","tid":2018754,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"都唔知你開個POST黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}